    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You strike with light but quick blows. This attack must be used as a follow-up to Taijutsu: Ougi - Rendan Kidouki, against the same target, gaining two additional attacks at a -5 penalty. These additional attacks cannot score critical hits, and you suffer a -6 penalty to confirming any critical hits with the other attacks.<br><br>If both additional attacks hit, the subject is knocked back 10 ft (Fortitude negates).</p>\n\n\n\n",
